precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 937) which
provides for the use of the "Lipase" enzyme made from the Aspergillus
oryzae strain, modified by recombinant DNA techniques, in the hydrolysis or
the modification of triglycerides (fats and oils).
